text: I am very touched by the messages from the children at the Sir Bobby Charlton Rehabilitation Centre in Amman. Our Foundation is ensuring that these children continue to be supported during the current pandemic. #Staystafe #Coronavirus#HumanitarianAid

Make sure to join the @SBCFoundation in our #SirBobbysHomeChampion initiative which brings together communities from across the globe to take part in a daily home exercise challenge. Looking forward to seeing how many of you get involved and become part of this great campaign.

These poignant pieces of art, created by young refugees undertaking art therapy at The SBCF Centre, showcases the horrors which thousands of children and adults have endured due to acts of terror and conflict. Please visit the gallery to learn about the children's experiences.
